pXmQPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJv705pXmQPM&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=91b398ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jv705pXmQPM</a><br />\n第40屆十大中文金曲 我和你音樂會<br />\n誠誠又係不得了半百歲人連跳三首爆舞歌真係抵佢紅透半邊天<br />\n陳仔結尾medley又係不得了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOzjx8L7KK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdOzjx8L7KK0&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=4e4c00a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOzjx8L7KK0</a><br />\n新城勁爆頒獎禮2017 <br />\n欣賞下rubberband suppermoment 呢兩隊真係勁有舞台感染力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜人在外國<br />\n之前有個音樂會《許志安與17安士音樂會》由許志安集結Chochukmo  Dear Jane  RubberBand 同Supper 搞到我都聽埋許志安 誠誠d歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_F8c9r49ZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc_F8c9r49ZM&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8ac5ce90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_F8c9r49ZM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gewHEZ1-40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0gewHEZ1-40&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=ca585372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gewHEZ1-40</a><br />\n梅艷芳 &bull; 10 &bull; 思念 &bull; 音樂會<br />\n呢個又係幾好睇可以睇到香港出到咁多天王巨星真係香港人驕傲<br />\n睇完呢個演唱會又儲落一堆梅艷芳 張國榮歌曲<br />\n<br />\n作為一個90後雖則過了外國無法經歷雨革但到依家本土意識真係前所未有咁旺盛<br />\nplaylist有9成半都係廣東歌<br />\n希望大家一齊擁護香港文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f831fe1d7c88a777eeb2f21579f0d12427ef3b","tid":631797,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2508b0d075c16cb75d64efc896e08b5f82351e2e","tid":631797,"uid":130814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T22:10:28.000Z","msg":"睇舊電影學下嘢