:"a8e68ed31d044bed3ed2241b7b2d89132fd4bb3b","tid":631797,"uid":130488,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T23:31:11.000Z","msg":"或者其實我唔應該推薦大家睇年代久遠電影始終都係太大effort <br />\n但在此真係想大家留意2014年開始嘅港產片<br />\n樹大招風真係絕世好片典型杜琪峰銀河映像電影講宿命 貪念 瞋念 痴念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一套係由杜琪峰 游乃海兩位監製三位新晉鮮浪潮導演 許學文 歐文傑 黃偉傑 以五年時間創os 各自執導三段故事剪輯而成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我太鐘意套戲但同時套戲太sad 到而家都唔太敢開第二次黎睇<br />\n最後茶樓一幕真係錦上添花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/072816_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F072816_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ee23d78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2deb2cb0d3a752c8dc8fbb7af57f0fdea8f8934","tid":631797,"uid":27939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"冇龍咁威就知個表係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daf7d3008fcdd84b7c334406f2c1f38186b7ec1","tid":631797,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f2bf81e2a8ce57cf8e6522cc5af6b8693b15c6","tid":631797,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a25862e9062be8bfcc730e3726c35ad14f681742","tid":631797,"uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T21:27:40.000Z","msg":"1916年？我屌你老母呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T22:04:04.000Z","msg":"認真我相信個個都會咁諗絕對包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我相信選得呢部出黎都有佢嘅原因<br />\n如果我有幸支撐到呢個地步睇完呢套戲再分享下點解呢套會咁高評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"呢套記錄片應該係睇1916年既香港影像，所以好珍貴"},{"pid":"fec13bae209a818c1